Subject: Rebrand startup/dashboard attribution to NadicodeAI

Replace the upstream "Nous Research" branding on the user-facing startup
and dashboard surfaces with Nadia/NadicodeAI product ownership. Upstream
provenance belongs in README/fork notices, not in the live CLI or desktop
product chrome. Surfaces:
  - ui-tui/src/components/branding.tsx — Ink TUI tagline + model-org line
  - hermes_cli/banner.py — rich CLI banner org token + credit line (plain
    text; NOT an OSC-8 link, so the banner's no-tag path stays hyperlink-free
    per tests/hermes_cli/test_banner.py)
  - web/src/components/SidebarFooter.tsx + web/src/i18n/*.ts (16 locales) —
    footer link (nadicode.ai) + org label
  - hermes_cli/dashboard_auth/login_page.py — login wordmark + product line

